data.name: Orichalcos Shunoros
data.desc: This card cannot be Normal Summoned or Set. If a Normal Monster you control is destroyed by battle, you can Special Summon this card from your hand. This card gains 1000 ATK for each monster your opponent controls. Face-up Level 4 Normal Monsters on the field cannot be destroyed by card effects.

card_sets.set_name: Dragons of Legend: The Complete Series
